Please nobody quote
that-- but I found

00:35:42.950 --> 00:35:46.390
a pasta making machine which
is more than 1,000 years old

00:35:46.390 --> 00:35:48.427
in northwest of Bhutan.

00:35:48.427 --> 00:35:50.260
And I'm going to show
you a picture of that.

00:35:50.260 --> 00:35:54.280
And it is like a
huge lemon press,

00:35:54.280 --> 00:35:56.300
like the lemon press
we have to squeeze

00:35:56.300 --> 00:35:58.310
lemon juice or the garlic press?

00:35:58.310 --> 00:36:00.010
They had this kind
of wooden thing.

00:36:00.010 --> 00:36:02.850
Now, this is that potato
noodles with chili paste.

00:36:02.850 --> 00:36:06.090
This is how she figured
out that there's

00:36:06.090 --> 00:36:09.680
a big block of potato
starch thing which

00:36:09.680 --> 00:36:12.000
was potato starch
just cooked in water

00:36:12.000 --> 00:36:14.490
and which was quite
