To make that for 1,000 bowls,
I think my hand will fall off.

00:36:47.651 --> 00:36:48.150
[LAUGHTER]

00:36:48.150 --> 00:36:52.790
VIKAS KHANNA: You know, practice
is what makes them so fast.

00:36:52.790 --> 00:36:54.290
One scrape, and bowl is ready.

00:36:54.290 --> 00:36:57.140
How fast she was.

