So I had this small computer
VAIO, that black one,

00:37:17.410 --> 00:37:19.410
the cheapest one I used to have.

00:37:19.410 --> 00:37:21.530
So I had everything
documented there,

00:37:21.530 --> 00:37:24.280
and this is the last
stop, 108 caves.

00:37:24.280 --> 00:37:25.790
So there was a
small place, which

00:37:25.790 --> 00:37:29.390
was like last time I'm
going to have butter tea.

00:37:29.390 --> 00:37:32.400
So I wanted to have my last
butter tea in total peace.

