So I ran out, and I forgot
my laptop in the bag next

00:37:47.630 --> 00:37:50.110
to my chair.

00:37:50.110 --> 00:37:53.404
And I forgot, and
I'm totally excited.

00:37:53.404 --> 00:37:55.570
And now I'm getting carried
away with the new sights

00:37:55.570 --> 00:37:56.380
and everything.

