It's the capital of Bhutan.

00:40:47.550 --> 00:40:49.536
This is actually the
only city in the world

00:40:49.536 --> 00:40:52.224
where there's no traffic lights.

00:40:52.224 --> 00:40:53.640
I think there's
one traffic signal

00:40:53.640 --> 00:40:56.540
in Bhutan, the whole
of the country.

00:40:56.540 --> 00:40:59.990
And nobody breaks traffic rules!

