They don't honk.

00:41:09.136 --> 00:41:10.670
They don't do anything.

00:41:10.670 --> 00:41:11.980
I don't know.

00:41:11.980 --> 00:41:13.730
It's a totally different
thought process,

00:41:13.730 --> 00:41:15.456
in which they say,
we don't honk,

00:41:15.456 --> 00:41:17.080
not to disturb the
other driver, but we

00:41:17.080 --> 00:41:19.180
don't honk to
disturb the nature.

00:41:19.180 --> 00:41:19.945
IRFAN DAMA: Wow.

00:41:19.945 --> 00:41:21.320
VIKAS KHANNA: So
I was like, wow.

00:41:21.320 --> 00:41:24.530
So this woman has this, and she
is making me the butter tea.

